Copy extplugin/limitcon.py to your b3 directory b3/extplugin and extplugin/conf/limitcon.xml to b3/extplugin/conf/.
Add the following line to b3/conf/b3.xml:
	<plugin config="@b3/extplugins/conf/limitcon.xml" name="limitcon" priority="12" />
Be aware that the priority is unique in your b3.xml.

Restart the bot.
